Quickstrike gave a violent start. His long, multi-fingered hand 
bristled. He spun around to see Inferno.

"What th' slaggin'...don't do that!" He glared at him, cocking his 
brows. He hadn't seen Inferno in a long while, and it sounded like he 
was aking for Megatron. "Royalty?"
